    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build and Explore</strong></h2><br>Explore a new zoo on every play-through. The game is gentle, but compelling, helping young players to learn how to explore digital spaces.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/ec5770c5b87d3f79712efdffd310e0db.poster.avif?t=1770239099\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/ec5770c5b87d3f79712efdffd310e0db.webm?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/ec5770c5b87d3f79712efdffd310e0db.mp4?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Learn Words</strong></h2><br>Alpha Zoo has 100 words to learn through typing. Children interact through the keyboard, and learn to spell and type words while playing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/ac5e3cf97192d4178c51b0ef71d828f8.poster.avif?t=1770239099\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/ac5e3cf97192d4178c51b0ef71d828f8.webm?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/ac5e3cf97192d4178c51b0ef71d828f8.mp4?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy a Rich World</strong></h2><br>Alpha Zoo has lots of surprises. Players delight as they discover they can make animals poop, re-color the train and ferris wheel, eat food in the cafe, or buy clothes and stuffed animals in the gift shop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/a996d525fd675e293f22e6c05e1e0194.poster.avif?t=1770239099\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/a996d525fd675e293f22e6c05e1e0194.webm?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/a996d525fd675e293f22e6c05e1e0194.mp4?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/51f0a588c208024b4e01716f17f85965.poster.avif?t=1770239099\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/51f0a588c208024b4e01716f17f85965.webm?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/51f0a588c208024b4e01716f17f85965.mp4?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/2e6026891f5a878e2f88f452b0d515cd.poster.avif?t=1770239099\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/2e6026891f5a878e2f88f452b0d515cd.webm?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/extras/2e6026891f5a878e2f88f452b0d515cd.mp4?t=1770239099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807640/